6, \"to\": 376}, {\"ngram\": \"a second\", \"from\": 380, \"to\": 388}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Watched from the stands by her three children at the Vaires-sur-Marne Nautical Stadium today, she won a third Olympic medal 12 years after the first of two golds but came up just short in her quest to become the first British mother to winrowinggold.\", \"from\": 391, \"to\": 641, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 444, \"end\": 460, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vaires-sur-Marne\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4367811370032732e-16, \"text\": \"Vaires-sur-Marne\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vaires-sur-Marne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vaires-sur-Marne\"}, {\"begin\": 609, \"end\": 616, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Television_in_the_United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.6004270556310781, \"rank\": 0.665446353585206, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Television_in_the_United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Television_in_the_United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the stands\", \"from\": 404, \"to\": 414}, {\"ngram\": \"her three children\", \"from\": 418, \"to\": 436}, {\"ngram\": \"a third Olympic medal\", \"from\": 493, \"to\": 514}, {\"ngram\": \"two golds\", \"from\": 543, \"to\": 552}, {\"ngram\": \"her quest\", \"from\": 579, \"to\": 588}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Twice she had retired and twice come back to the sport hoping to act as inspiration for her fellow mums but also six-year-old son Logan and her four-year-old twins Willow and Kit.\", \"from\": 643, \"to\": 822, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 773, \"end\": 778, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Logan_City\", \"score\": 0.5490278365478093, \"rank\": 0.8205598431680973, \"text\": \"Logan\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Logan_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Logan_City\"}, {\"begin\": 807, \"end\": 813, \"title\": \"http: